"RESTful API 是利用 `FastAPI <https://github.com/tiangolo/fastapi>`_ 實作的，具體程式碼在 "
"`api/restful_api.py "
"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference/tree/main/xinference/api/restful_api.py>`_。"

#: ../../source/development/xinference_internals.rst:35
